<type>(<scope>): <summary>

Types: feat, fix, docs, test, refactor, perf, build, ci, chore, release
Scope: short kebab-case area, for example release, demo, cli, opencode
Summary: imperative/lowercase start, <= 72 characters including header

Examples:
docs(release): require bilingual release notes
test(sample): make agent CLI detection deterministic
release: v0.6.2
